metadata.source: SF Ethics Commission - Permit Consultant Disclosure Registry
notes: Permit consultants must register with the SF Ethics Commission under S.F. Campaign & Governmental Conduct Code Section 3.400 et seq.
This registry includes both original registrations and amendments.
Some consultants appear multiple times due to amendments or re-registrations.
DBI expediter stats come from dataset 3pee-9qhc, querying role='pmt consultant/expediter'.
